org.openstack4j.openstack.internal

Class OSClientSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openstack4j.openstack.internal.OSClientSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EndpointTokenProvider, OSClient

    public class OSClientSession
extends Object
implements OSClient, EndpointTokenProvider
    A client which has been identified. Any calls spawned from this session will automatically utilize the original authentication that was successfully validated and authorized
    Author:
    Jeremy Unruh
